    <p>We did a lot of in-house testing with the remote to see how people felt about the responsiveness and process of changing a TV screen. There a still many ideas we have for the remote and even collaboration from the TV display to the users web application. </p>

    <h3>The Result</h3>

    <p>We now have two customers who have bought Situation Rooms and a lot of other companies who have expressed interest. </p>

